fields.physical_description:
[box] top opening card box printed in colours to show the title, maker's details and illustrations of the character animals and the game itself; also a photograph of a single figure with the stamps of the Toy of the Year Award
the bottom of the box is printed with the rules and a list of other games by the publishers
[box lining] pre formed white plastic tray with central well housing the smaller pieces and cards
[board] card printed in colours to show the title, game layout, characters and directions, together with the maker's name
at the centre are two folds, creating a book like effect which is different from the normal board games
reverse side is pale blue grey
[family card] thin white card printed to show 6 rectangular spaces surrounded by a red line and a pale blue and white border; title at the top and family name at the bottom
